"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:341:\"Cm n anh ch em  tham d WordPress Meetup ti H Ni thng 07/2023.  trn mt nm mi thy s quay tr li ca Meetup, v s nhit thnh, cng nhau ng gp, trao i  khi dy rt nhiu nng lng cho mi ngi. Trong bui hm nay, i din t Code [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Khoi Pro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5802:\"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-2.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"767\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-2-1024x767.png\" alt=\"WordPress Meetup H Ni thng 07/2023\" class=\"wp-image-1081\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-2-1024x767.png 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-2-300x225.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-2-768x575.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-2-440x330.png 440w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-2.png 1276w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Cm n anh ch em  tham d WordPress Meetup ti H Ni thng 07/2023.  trn mt nm mi thy s quay tr li ca Meetup, v s nhit thnh, cng nhau ng gp, trao i  khi dy rt nhiu nng lng cho mi ngi.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-1078\"></span>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1024x569.png\" alt=\"Ti u Web mi nht t Code Tt\" class=\"wp-image-1079\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1024x569.png 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-300x167.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-768x427.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image.png 1094w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong bui hm nay, i din t Code Tt  chia s nhng nh hng ti u web hiu qu v c mc, ng mc ch, t kt qu.  khng ch l vic ti u PageSpeed Web, m l tng th phi xc nh mc tiu dng website vo vic g v cc bc tin hnh ra sao.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"572\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-1024x572.png\" alt=\"Tm hiu v ReactJS, NextJS\" class=\"wp-image-1080\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-1024x572.png 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-300x168.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1-768x429.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/07/image-1.png 1291w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p> phn chia s ca anh Hong t Melisoft v m hnh NextJS s dng API t bn th ba (nh WordPress REST API), tp trung vo vic xoay quanh m hnh m-un ho, tinh chnh lin tc, to ra nhng nn tng c mc  ti s dng cao. Anh Hong cng  gii thiu mt s kin trc c pht trin v to ra MeliPlatform kh th v, nhn c s quan tm ca mi ngi thng qua s cu hi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mt s cu hi khc v WordPress cng c gii p v trao i kh nhit tnh.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Vic nh k nng cp website WordPress l cn thit, c bit l cc phin bn Minor (nh dng x.x.[x]). Cc phin bn Major th cn tin hnh sao lu trc khi nng cp.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Nn s dng cc plugin bo mt gip hn ch tn cng nh Wordfence.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vic s dng kt hp gia NextJS v WP REST API c nhng mc tiu c th, c bit l phi quan tm ti i tng s dng chnh l ai.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Xu hng ChatGPT p dng trong cng vic digital marketing.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vic ti u website ph thuc nhiu vo ti nguyn, chi ph, v c nhiu gii php khc nhau. Tuy nhin, vic hng ti pht trin vi ngun lc u t ph hp l hng i ng n nht cho doanh nghip.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tham gia cc s kin tip theo</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cc Meetup tip theo ti H Ni c cng b trn nhm Zalo: <a href=\"https://zalo.me/g/gfqysr978\">https://zalo.me/g/gfqysr978</a> (ni bn s c chn ch , thi gian, a im).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Slide chng trnh:</strong><br>&#8211; <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1ZNT9RDVyoBHXYN08LusDfeAKp1RCGYsm1OZBVDUZJm8/edit?fbclid=IwAR39tITgZOJHvC_j2u-Ty7I3SpIZXagPce8mIlZVxmsCKDkr9av4O73tN5I\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1ZNT9RDVyoBHXYN08LusDfeAKp1RCGYsm1OZBVDUZJm8/edit?fbclid=IwAR39tITgZOJHvC_j2u-Ty7I3SpIZXagPce8mIlZVxmsCKDkr9av4O73tN5I\">Ti u web mi nht</a>, t Mr. Khi (Founder/CEO Code Tt)<br>&#8211; Chia s v <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/hLFfSDh2GihHNAhPDyMA5w/Melisoft---Reactjs\">React+NextJS</a> t Mr. Hong (Founder/CEO Melisoft) <br>&#8211; Qu tng thm 1 bi vit v <a href=\"https://codetot.vn/inp/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://codetot.vn/inp/\">INP</a>  mi ngi c lc qua ni dung cp nht mi nht.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cm n phn ti tr nc ung t nh cung cp Hosting InterData, ti tr a im ca <a href=\"https://codetot.vn/ve-code-tot/\">Code Tt</a>, s tham gia t cc cng ng <strong>Yu SEO</strong>, <strong>SEO Meetup</strong>, <strong>CxO H Ni</strong>, nhm <strong><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/toiuuweb/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/toiuuweb/\">Ti u web </a></strong>  c c nhng kt ni tham gia.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2023/07/22/recap-wordpress-meetup-ha-noi-thang-07-2023/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0