(17, 1, '2024-04-14 17:01:55', '2024-04-14 17:01:55', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1. HP NG</strong>&nbsp; Cc iu khon v iu kin ny - cng vi bt k iu khon b sung no khc bng vn bn m chng ti cung cp cho bn lin quan n tha thun t hng hoc dch v ca bn - to thnh hp ng gia bn - ngi mua thit b c th (bao gm c cc b phn v hng ha khc), giy php phn mm v/hoc dch v (\"Ngi Mua\") vi chng ti - n v Mettler-Toledo ghi r trong bn bo gi, th xc nhn n t hng, tha thun dch v, ha n hoc ti liu t hng khc chng ti giao cho bn (\"MT\"). Cc quyn v ngha v ghi r trong hp ng ny p dng cho Ngi Mua  mua thit b, giy php phn mm v cc dch v c ghi r trong cc ti liu t hng ca MT. Nu n t hng ca Ngi Mua bao gm phn mm bt buc phi tun th tha thun giy php ngi dng cui (\"EULA\"), cc iu khon ca EULA cng p dng v c u tin so vi cc iu khon ny. Cc iu khon v iu kin khc nhau hoc khc vi cc iu khon v iu kin ny s ch p dng nu c hai bn u ng  bng vn bn. Cc iu khon hoc iu kin bao gm trong cc biu mu ca Ngi Mua, k c cc iu khon v iu kin mua hng chun ca Ngi Mua v cc ti liu xut trnh cho cc i din dch v ti ch ca MT u khng phi l mt phn ca hp ng ny. Bin nhn thit b, giy php phn mm ca Ngi Mua v/hoc cc dch v cho php chp nhn hon ton cc iu khon v iu kin ny cng nh mi EULA p dng c sn ti&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mt.com/legal\">www.mt.com/legal</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2. CP PHP</strong>&nbsp; Nu khng c EULA, MT s cp cho Ngi Mua quyn hn khng c quyn, khng ti cp php v khng th chuyn nhng  s dng phn mm  t hng ch cho cc mc ch ni b ca Ngi Mua. Ngi mua khng c thit k ngc, dch ngc hay tho ri bt c phn mm no  c MT cp php.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>3. BO GI, GI CNG B V THNG TIN SN PHM</strong>&nbsp; Bo gi v cc u i bn hng khc t ng ht hn sau 30 ngy k t ngy ban hnh, tr khi c nu r theo cch khc v tr khi MT rt li bn bo gi hoc u i bn hng  bt c lc no trc khi Ngi Mua chp nhn bn bo gi hoc u i . Bo gi v cc u i lin quan n thit b hoc phn mm ty chnh c th da trn mt s thng tin v tnh hung nht nh, bao gm cc thng tin m Ngi Mua cung cp. Khi cc thng tin hoc tnh hung m MT  da trn   a ra bn bo gi hoc u i bn hng thay i th MT c th iu chnh bn bo gi hoc u i . Gi cng b khng phi l gi bn v c th thay i m khng cn thng bo. MT c th thay i thng s k thut thit b hoc phn mm m khng thng bo tr khi cng ty ng  vi (cc) thng s k thut bng vn bn. Gi khng bao gm bt k khon thu, ph vn chuyn, ph ng gi, ph x l, bo him, thu, ph kim tra, ph cp php, chi ph lp t no hay cc chi ph hoc dch v khc tr khi c nu r theo cch khc trong cc ti liu t hng. MT c th quyt nh chp nhn hoc t chi bt c n hng no; MT-M s n t hng: (a) km theo vn bn xc nhn n t hng; hoc (b) khi thc hin n t hng. c tnh sn phm c th - bao gm nhng khng gii hn  trng lng sn phm, kch thc, gi tr, t l hon vn u t, trng ti, dung sai v cc d liu k thut khc khng m bo cc c tnh  v c cung cp ch  tham kho. Ngi Mua khng c tit l bt k bn bo gi, mc gi, thng s k thut hoc thng tin sn phm no cho bt k bn th ba no m khng c s ng  trc bng vn bn ca MT.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>4. THU&nbsp;</strong> Nu lut php a phng bt buc MT thu ca Ngi Mua bt k khon thu no, n s c thm vo ha n ca Ngi Mua v Ngi Mua s chu trch nhim thanh ton khon thu , tr khi Ngi Mua cung cp cho MT giy chng nhn min thu hp l. Nu giy chng nhn min thu m Ngi Mua cung cp cho MT sau  c xc nh l khng hp l th Ngi Mua s phi tr khon thu cha thanh ton trc y.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>5. IU KHON THANH TON</strong>&nbsp; iu khon thanh ton c nu r trong cc ti liu t hng ca MT. Nu khng nu r iu khon thanh ton th thi hn thanh ton l trn 30 ngy k t ngy lp ho n. Ngi Mua khng c gi li bt k khon thanh ton no m h cn n MT theo hp ng ny, hay mt khc  ring bt c khon tin no m h n MT theo hp ng ny,  khiu ni tranh chp.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>6. VN CHUYN, X L V GIAO HNG</strong>&nbsp; iu khon vn chuyn c nu r trong cc ti liu t hng ca MT. Nu khng nu r iu khon vn chuyn th p dng phng thc Giao hng ti xng. Ngy giao hng v ngy s dng dch v ch l ngy c tnh tr khi MT ng  r bng vn bn mt ngy hoc mt lch trnh c nh. MT s tin hnh cc n lc thng mi hp l  p ng ngy giao hng v ngy s dng dch v c tnh. Tt c cc ngy giao hng v ngy s dng dch v ty thuc vo vic MT kp thi nhn c ton b thng tin v s chp thun cn thit. Nu Ngi Mua khin vic giao hng b chm tr, MT s lu gi v x l tt c cc mt hng vi ri ro thuc v Ngi Mua, v s lp ha n cho Ngi Mua i vi phn gi hp ng cha thanh ton cng vi gi lu kho, bo him v chi ph x l p dng. MT c th giao hng tng t. MT s khng chu trch nhim v bt k s thiu ht hay thit hi no tr khi Ngi Mua gi li tt c cc container vn chuyn v vt liu ng gi  kim tra.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>7. TR HNG</strong>&nbsp; Thit b hoc giy php phn mm c thit k, sa i, ty chnh hoc nh cu hnh c bit cho Ngi Mua th khng th tr li, tr khi c yu cu bo hnh hp l m thit b hoc phn mm  khng th sa cha. Ngi Mua khng th tr li thit b  c thay i, b hng,  qua s dng hoc  lp t trc . Tr khi MT gy ra li vn chuyn hoc Ngi Mua a ra yu cu bo hnh hp l, thit b xut xng nhng cha s dng mi c hon tr ch khi Ngi Mua lin h vi MT  c chp thun v hng dn hon tr trc khi tin hnh hon tr bt c sn phm no. MT c quyn tnh ph hon kho cho Ngi Mua i vi mi sn phm hon tr.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>8. HY N HNG</strong>&nbsp; Khi c vn bn chp thun ca MT, Ngi Mua c th hy n hng trc khi vn chuyn thit b hoc phn mm hoc trc khi bt u k kt hp ng dch v. MT c th hy n hng ca Ngi Mua hoc yu cu thanh ton trc nu Ngi Mua chuyn giao ti sn v li ch ca cc ch n, hoc nu MT c l do  tin rng Ngi Mua khng sn sng hoc khng th thc hin cam kt ca mnh. Nu Ngi Mua hy n hng khc vi trng hp cho php  phn ny th Ngi Mua phi tr cho MT ton b cc khon tin phi tr theo n t hng. Nu n hng ca Ngi Mua b hy v bt c l do g, Ngi Mua s phi tr cho MT cc chi ph v ph tn hp l (bao gm chi ph thit k v ton b cam kt vi cc nh cung cp cng nh nh thu ph ca MT) pht sinh trc khi MT nhn c thng bo hy n hng cng vi t l li nhun thng thng ca MT cho sn phm tng t. Ph hy n hng ti thiu l 15% mc gi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>9. THAY I N HNG</strong>&nbsp; Ngi Mua c th thay i n hng nu c MT chp thun bng vn bn. Nhm p ng yu cu thay i n hng ca Ngi Mua, MT c th thay i gi c v lch giao hng. Nu MT  tin hnh cng vic hoc mua sn cc vt liu nhm phc v n hng ca Ngi Mua v yu cu thay i ca Ngi Mua khin cho cng vic hoc cc vt liu  tr nn khng cn thit na th Ngi Mua vn phi chu trch nhim thanh ton cc chi ph .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>10. LI CH BO M</strong>&nbsp; Ngi Mua cp cho MT li ch bo m trn ti sn mua trong giy php thit b v phn mm m h  mua, tha nhn tnh hp l ca s cp php ny v ng  khng phn i tnh hp php ca s cp php ny. Ngi Mua s h tr MT trong vic thc hin tt c cc hot ng cn thit  hon thin v bo v li ch bo m ca MT. MT c hng bt k mi quyn li v bin php khc phc theo quy nh ca php lut hoc theo vn ch s hu ch khi Ngi Mua mc nh chp nhn iu  trong ngha v ca h i vi MT.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>11. Bo hnh: NU KHNG CP CHO NGI MUA VN BN QUY NH CHNH SCH BO HNH RING, MT BO M R RNG THIT B, PHN MM V DCH V CA MNH L DUY NHT NH NU R  PHN NY. N MT MC  TI A C LUT PHP CHO PHP, MT T CHI A RA MI TUYN B BO M NO D L R RNG HAY NG  (BAO GM NHNG KHNG GII HN  CC BO M V KH NNG THNG MI HAY TNH THNG THCH CHO CHO MT MC CH C TH). CC BO M NY CH C CHUYN GIAO CHO NGI MUA THIT B SAU  HOC CHO NGI C CP PHP PHN MM SAU  KHI C VN BN CHP THUN TRC CA MT. NGOI RA, CC BO M SAU CU THNH CC BIN PHP KHC PHC DUY NHT V C QUYN CA NGI MUA I VI MI VI PHM CA MT TRONG CHNH SCH BO HNH NY.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A. THIT B</strong>&nbsp; MT bo m rng trong iu kin s dng bnh thng: (i) thit b ca mnh - ngoi tr cc b phn thay th - s khng b li tay ngh v vt liu trong vng 1 nm k t ngy lp t/s dng ban u hoc trong vng 18 thng k t ngy c MT giao hng, bt k iu no xy ra trc; v (ii) cc b phn thay th s khng b li tay ngh v vt liu trong vng 90 ngy k t ngy giao hng. Nu cc li va m t c tm thy v bo co