15% mc gi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>9. THAY I N HNG</strong>&nbsp; Ngi Mua c th thay i n hng nu c MT chp thun bng vn bn. Nhm p ng yu cu thay i n hng ca Ngi Mua, MT c th thay i gi c v lch giao hng. Nu MT  tin hnh cng vic hoc mua sn cc vt liu nhm phc v n hng ca Ngi Mua v yu cu thay i ca Ngi Mua khin cho cng vic hoc cc vt liu  tr nn khng cn thit na th Ngi Mua vn phi chu trch nhim thanh ton cc chi ph .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>10. LI CH BO M</strong>&nbsp; Ngi Mua cp cho MT li ch bo m trn ti sn mua trong giy php thit b v phn mm m h  mua, tha nhn tnh hp l ca s cp php ny v ng  khng phn i tnh hp php ca s cp php ny. Ngi Mua s h tr MT trong vic thc hin tt c cc hot ng cn thit  hon thin v bo v li ch bo m ca MT. MT c hng bt k mi quyn li v bin php khc phc theo quy nh ca php lut hoc theo vn ch s hu ch khi Ngi Mua mc nh chp nhn iu  trong ngha v ca h i vi MT.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>11. Bo hnh: NU KHNG CP CHO NGI MUA VN BN QUY NH CHNH SCH BO HNH RING, MT BO M R RNG THIT B, PHN MM V DCH V CA MNH L DUY NHT NH NU R  PHN NY. N MT MC  TI A C LUT PHP CHO PHP, MT T CHI A RA MI TUYN B BO M NO D L R RNG HAY NG  (BAO GM NHNG KHNG GII HN  CC BO M V KH NNG THNG MI HAY TNH THNG THCH CHO CHO MT MC CH C TH). CC BO M NY CH C CHUYN GIAO CHO NGI MUA THIT B SAU  HOC CHO NGI C CP PHP PHN MM SAU  KHI C VN BN CHP THUN TRC CA MT. NGOI RA, CC BO M SAU CU THNH CC BIN PHP KHC PHC DUY NHT V C QUYN CA NGI MUA I VI MI VI PHM CA MT TRONG CHNH SCH BO HNH NY.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A. THIT B</strong>&nbsp; MT bo m rng trong iu kin s dng bnh thng: (i) thit b ca mnh - ngoi tr cc b phn thay th - s khng b li tay ngh v vt liu trong vng 1 nm k t ngy lp t/s dng ban u hoc trong vng 18 thng k t ngy c MT giao hng, bt k iu no xy ra trc; v (ii) cc b phn thay th s khng b li tay ngh v vt liu trong vng 90 ngy k t ngy giao hng. Nu cc li va m t c tm thy v bo co trong thi hn bo hnh, MT s c quyn la chn hon tin bng ng gi mua, thay th thit b hoc sa cha cc li  bng cch cung cp cc b phn thay th v min ph nhn cng thc hin. Vn chuyn ti 80 km (50 dm) tnh t i din dch v gn nht ca chng ti hoc nh cung cp dch v y quyn s c hon ton min ph cho yu cu bo hnh hp l.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>B. PHN MM</strong>&nbsp; Nu c ci t ng theo thng s k thut v cc yu cu h thng, MT m bo phn mm m cng ty pht trin s thc hin ng k cc chc nng c m t trong ti liu phn mm m cng ty cung cp hay mt khc nh c tha thun bng vn bn trong trng hp khng c bt k ti liu phn mm no. MT khng bo m phn mm khng b li, rng Ngi Mua c th s dng phn mm khng b gin on, rng giao din ca bn th ba hoc cc h thng kt ni vi phn mm s hot ng khng b gin on hoc phn mm s khng c l hng  xm nhp hoc tn cng. Nu MT khng cp cho Ngi Mua vn bn quy nh chnh sch bo hnh ring th thi hn bo hnh phn mm vn hnh thit b cng bng thi hn bo hnh thit b c mua cng vi phn mm . Thi hn bo hnh cho bt k phn mm hay tnh nng phn mm no khc l 90 ngy k t ngy giao hng.  trnh s nghi ng, chnh sch bo hnh ca chng ti bao gm sa li nhng khng bao gm bt k tnh nng mi no. Tr khi c tha thun khc bng vn bn, MT khng c chnh sch bo hnh cho phn mm c pht trin, sa i hay ty chnh ring cho Ngi Mua. Cc chnh sch bo hnh ny cng c p dng cho mi phin bn v dch v mi m MT c th cung cp trong tng lai.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>C. DCH V</strong>&nbsp; MT bo m rng cc dch v s c thc hin theo cch thc chuyn nghip ph hp vi thng l chun ca ngnh cng nghip. Nu bt k s khng ph hp no c pht hin trong vng 30 ngy k t ngy sn phm c hon tt v Ngi Mua kp thi thng bo cho MT bng vn bn, MT s cung cp dch v, thng tin hng dn hoc tham vn cn thit  khc phc s khng ph hp .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>D. IU KHON CHUNG</strong>&nbsp; Cc bo m nu trn cn ty thuc vo cc iu kin chung sau y: (i) Vt t, ph kin, hao mn thng thng, cc b phn hao mn v d hng c loi tr r. (ii) Nu Ngi Mua yu cu bo hnh trong thi gian lm vic ngoi tiu chun th Ngi Mua s b tnh ph cho thi gian ph tri. (iii) Cc bo m ny khng p dng khi thit b v/hoc phn mm ca MT  b: tai nn, thay i, s dng sai mc ch, lm dng, do Ngi Mua khng m bo quy trnh bo qun, vn hnh v/hoc bo dng, lp t hay bo tr ng quy cch m nhn vin MT khng cho php, b sung hoc cung cp thit b hay phn mm khng c chp thun  tch hp vo sn phm ca MT, iu kin mi trng hoc iu kin hot ng, hoc phn mm hay giao din m Ngi Mua hoc bn th ba cung cp v bt k mi l do no khc m MT khng chu trch nhim. (iv) MT khng bo m tnh hiu chun ca mi thit b. Tuy nhin, MT bo m thit b ca mnh c th c iu chnh  p ng cc thng s k thut  in trong ti liu ca MT, nu c,  t  chnh xc trong thi hn bo hnh ni trn khi c lp t v s dng ng quy cch. (v) Sn phm ca cc nh sn xut khc m MT bn ch c MT bo hnh trong phm vi ca mi thi hn bo hnh cn li c cung cp bi nh sn xut gc . (vi) Nu MT sa cha thit b th cng vic sa cha  s khng ko di thm thi hn bo hnh hin ti cng nh khng to ra thi hn bo hnh mi cho ton b thit b hay cho nhng phn khng c MT sa cha hoc thay th. Tr khi Ngi Mua gi cho MT vn bn thng bo trc v MT ng  rng chnh sch bo hnh ca mnh vn ang p dng, ton b mi chnh sch bo hnh u l v hiu nu sn phm c a ra khi quc gia m MT  giao hng n.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>E. BIN PHP KHC PHC LI TRONG THI HN BO HNH</strong>&nbsp; MT c th c gng chn on v gii quyt cc li  qua in thoi hoc qua th in t. Mt s thit b tch hp cc tnh nng h tr t xa  bo co trc tip vn , xc nh vn  t xa v bin php khc phc. Khi lin h vi MT v vic bo hnh, Ngi Mua phi tun th quy trnh xc nh vn , bin php khc phc v quy trnh m MT nu r. MT c th yu cu gi li mt phn hoc ton b thit b v kho ca mnh  sa cha hoc h tr xc nh vn . Nu MT xc nh cn phi tin hnh cng vic sa cha ti ch th mt k thut vin sa cha s c sp xp. Nu Ngi Mua thng bo cho MT v mt li no  v yu cu sa cha ti ch trong khi li  c th c khc phc t xa, hoc nu MT phc p cho thng bo li  ca Ngi Mua v khng tm thy li no m MT chu trch nhim th MT s c bi thng cho mi cng vic  thc hin v mi chi ph  gnh chu do yu cu ca Ngi Mua. Vic khng lp t v s dng cc cng c v thit b kt ni t xa sn c  bo co vn  trc tip, xc nh vn  t xa v khc phc vn  c th dn n thi gian p ng lu v khin Ngi Mua phi chu thm chi ph.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>12. BI THNG</strong>&nbsp; MT s bi thng cho Ngi Mua cc khon tin m Ngi Mua b tn tht pht sinh trc tip do thng tt c th (k c t vong) ca bn th ba hoc thit hi ti sn ca bn th ba trong trng hp b thng hoc b thit hi: (i) xy ra trong qu trnh lm vic ca MT; (ii) xy ra ti c s ca Ngi Mua; v (iii) hon ton gy ra do hnh vi bt cn hoc thiu st ca MT. Cc tn tht m MT bi thng c th bao gm chi ph php l hp l v quyt ton ca v khiu ni hay kin tng. Ngha v bi thng ca MT cho cc tn tht ca Ngi Mua ch pht sinh nu Ngi Mua kp thi thng bo cho MT bng vn bn v cc tn tht  da trn c s khi Ngi Mua  c tnh hp l thit hi . Khi yu cu MT bi thng tn tht, Ngi Mua cho php MT c ton quyn duy nht trong vic x l bin h i vi bt k khiu ni no lin quan n MT, v MT c y quyn gii quyt hoc ha gii cc khiu ni  theo ton quyn duy nht; v Ngi Mua phi hp tc trong vic bin h tt c cc khiu ni  khi MT xt thy l cn thit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>13. VI PHM BNG SNG CH</strong>&nbsp; MT s bin h cho bt k v kin no chng li Ngi Mua nu n da trn tuyn b hp l rng thit b hoc phn mm do MT thit k  c Ngi Mua mua theo hp ng ny hoc bt c phn no lin quan l s vi phm bt k bng sng ch hin hnh no. Ngha v ca MT ch pht sinh khi: (a) Ngi Mua kp thi thng bo cho MT bng vn bn v tuyn b  v y quyn cho MT, cung cp thng tin v s h tr cn thit  bin h chng li tuyn b ; v (b) vi phm b co buc khng phi l kt qu ca mt thit k hoc yu cu c bit khc m Ngi Mua quy nh hoc l kt qu ca vic Ngi Mua hay ngi khc p dng hay s dng thit b hoc phn mm . MT s ch bi thng mi thit hi v chi ph m Ngi Mua cui cng b pht khi MT c ton quyn bin h, gii quyt hoc ha gii v kin v Ngi Mua khng thc hin bt c hnh ng no lm nh hng n kh nng ca MT trong vic tin hnh bin h, gii quyt hoc ha gii hiu qu. Khi c Ngi Mua thng bo v co buc rng thit b, phn mm hoc mt b phn no  vi phm bt k bng sng ch no, vi chi ph v la chn ca mnh, MT c th: (i) cho php Ngi Mua tip tc s dng thit b, phn mm hoc b phn ; (ii) Ci t cc ng dng tin tin  nng cao hiu qu ca cc thit b hoc phn mm; (iii) sa i thit b, phn mm hoc b phn   n tr thnh khng vi phm; hoc (iv) loi b thit b, phn mm hoc b phn  v hon tin bng ng gi mua cng nh ton b chi ph vn chuyn v lp t lin quan. y l ton b trch nhim ca MT i vi Ngi Mua trong trng hp vi phm bn quyn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>14. LUT PHP V/HOC CC TIU CHUN QUY NH</strong>&nbsp; MT tun th cc quy nh php lut c lin quan. MT cng tin hnh cc bc hp l  lun bo m thit b ca mnh ph hp vi cc tiu chun v quy nh m vn c th p dng khi Ngi Mua s dng cc sn phm ca MT. Tuy nhin, thit b ca MT c s dng trong nhiu ng dng quy nh v i khi cc tiu chun v quy nh li khng thng nht vi nhau. MT khng cam kt hoc tuyn b rng thit b ca mnh s tun th mi lut php, quy nh, quy chun hay tiu chun, tr khi c quy nh r v c thng nht bng vn bn bi mt quan chc c thm quyn. Ngi Mua c trch nhim lp t, vn hnh v hiu chnh thit b ng quy cch ph hp vi tt c cc lut php v quy nh hin hnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>15. S TAY HNG DN S DNG SN PHM</strong>&nbsp; Ngi Mua phi tun th thng tin lp t, s tay hng dn s dng sn phm v h thng, hng dn vn hnh v an ton cng nh cc ti liu v thng s k thut khc m MT cung cp km theo thit b; MT khc t mi trch nhim php l - bao gm trch nhim bo hnh - nu Ngi Mua khng tun th mi hng dn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>16. QUYN S HU TR TU</strong>&nbsp; Tr khi MT ng  r iu ngc li bng vn bn, MT khng chuyn giao cho Ngi Mua bt c quyn s hu no cho bt k bng sng ch, bn quyn, thng hiu, cng ngh, thit k, thng s k thut, bn v hay ti sn tr tu no khc lin quan n thit b, phn mm v/hoc dch v. Tr khi c nu r theo cch khc trong EULA p dng, cc quyn cp php phn mm c cp l khng c quyn, khng ti cp php, khng th chuyn nhng v mang tnh gii hn  ch s dng cho cc mc ch  c thng nht.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>17. KHC T TRCH NHIM BI THNG THIT HI TRONG BT C TRNG HP NO, MT CNG KHNG CHU TRCH NHIM VI NGI MUA HOC VI BT K BN NO KHC V MI LOI THIT HI C BIT, THIT HI DO HU QU, THIT HI GIN TIP, THIT HI BT NG, THIT HI IN HNH HOC THIT HI DO B PHT, CHO D CC THIT HI  PHT SINH DO HOC L KT QU CA VIC VI PHM HP NG, CHNH SCH BO HNH, SAI LM C NHN (BAO GM S SUT) CNG NH KHNG CHU TRCH NHIM PHP L NGHIM NGT HAY NI CCH KHC L BT K HP NG C T C HAY KHNG T C MC CH CN THIT.&nbsp;</strong>Cc thit hi ny bao gm nhng khng gii hn  vic tht thot li nhun hoc doanh thu, mt quyn s dng thit b hoc thit b v phn mm c lin quan, tn chi ph thay th thit b hoc phn mm, c s vt cht, chi ph cho thi gian cht, tng chi ph xy dng, nh hng n uy tn, mt khch hng cc hoc khiu ni t pha khch hng hoc nh thu ca Ngi Mua i vi cc thit hi . Ngi Mua khng c chuyn nhng, chuyn giao hoc cho thu thit b hay phn mm c bn hoc c cp php theo hp ng ny cho bt k bn th ba no m trc ht khng m bo rng h cng phi bo v cho MT  phn ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>18. GII HN TRCH NHIM</strong>&nbsp; MT khng chu trch nhim v mi tn tht, khiu ni, chi ph hoc thit hi gy ra bi, gp phn vo hoc pht sinh do cc hnh vi hay thiu st ca Ngi Mua hoc bn th ba, cho d l s sut hoc theo cch khc. Trong bt c trng hp no, tng trch nhim ca MT i vi bt k v ton b mi loi thit hi hay tn tht lin quan n hp ng ny hoc n thit b, phn mm hay dch v c bn, c cp php hoc c giao hng theo y cng khng vt qu gi ca sn phm dn n khiu ni, cho d cn c vo hp ng, chnh sch bo hnh, bi thng hoc sai lm c nhn (k c s sut). V bt k v kin no pht sinh sau y phi c bt u trong vng 1 nm k t ngy bt ngun nguyn nhn ca v kin .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>19. KHNG C TRCH NHIM CUNG CP THNG TIN HOC H TR MIN PH</strong>&nbsp; Tr khi xuyn tc la o, MT khng c trch nhim cung cp cho Ngi Mua bt k thng tin, s h tr hoc t vn no nu thng tin, s h tr hoc t vn  l khng bt buc theo hp ng ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>20. BO 