u .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>24. LUT P DNG V NI C THM QUYN XT X</strong>&nbsp; Vic thc hin ca cc bn theo hp ng ny v mi quan h gia cc bn tun th lut php hin hnh ca quc gia ni t vn phng m Mettler Toledo ghi r trong cc ti liu t hng ca MT; Nu vn phng Mettler Toledo ghi r trong cc ti liu t hng &nbsp;ca MT t ti Hoa K th lut php ca Tiu bang Delaware s c p dng. Ni duy nht gii quyt cc khiu ni pht sinh theo hp ng ny l ta n c thm quyn gn nht vi ni t vn phng m Mettler Toledo ghi r trong cc ti liu t hng ca MT; Nu vn phng Mettler Toledo ghi r trong cc ti liu t hng ca MT t ti Hoa K th ta n Tiu bang Delaware l ni gii quyt duy nht. Tuy nhin, MT c quyn khi kin Ngi Mua ti bt k ta n no khc c thm quyn. Cng c Lin Hip Quc v Hp ng Mua bn Hng ha Quc t c loi tr r.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>25. WEEE</strong>&nbsp; Khi c yu cu bi lut php hin hnh, MT s vt b rc thi thit b in v in t (WEEE) theo chi ph ca Ngi Mua.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>26. TRUY TM NGUN GC</strong>&nbsp; Ngi Mua xc nhn MT c quyn truy tm ngun gc hoc thu hi thit b hoc tin hnh cc bin php khc phc khc i vi thit b . Ngi Mua s tch cc h tr MT khi pht sinh nhu cu ny. Nu Ngi Mua bn li thit b cho bn th ba th Ngi Mua s c xem l nh phn phi thit b ny theo lut php hin hnh v phi tun th mi ngha v lin quan km theo, bao gm nhng khng gii hn : (i) lu gi tt c cc ti liu v thng tin cn thit  truy tm ngun gc hoc thu hi thit b  bn cho bn th ba  ti thiu 10 nm; (ii) thng bo ngay cho MT v bt k mi khiu ni hay s c bt li lin quan n thit b v kp thi tun th tt c cc hng dn ca MT lin quan n vic iu tra hoc x l vn ; v (iii) tun th tt c cc ngha v bo qun v vn chuyn hin ang p dng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>27. D LIU C NHN V THNG TIN KHC</strong>&nbsp; Ngi Mua ng  rng MT c quyn s dng, x l, lu tr v cho php bn th ba thay mt cho MT s dng, x l v lu tr bt k d liu no m MT thu thp c trong hp ng ny theo quy nh ca lut php lin quan. Tr khi c tha thun t bit trong n t hng vi MT, hng ha v dch v ca chng ti s khng bao gm bt c quy trnh cung cp thng tin c nhn ca MT cho bn Mua. Trong quy chun v mi quan h vi i tc, chng ti c th x l hn ch cc thng tin c nhn ca mt s nhn vin ca i tc, hay nh thu  c th p ng yu cu ca i tc, v  thc hin hp ng vi i tc (v d  x l v thc hin n hng, x l vic thanh ton, sp xp giao hng, v cung cp dch v sa cha, h tr).&nbsp;<strong>MT s s dng thng tin lin h chi tit nhn c t i tc trong ti liu mua hng ha v dch v cho cc hot ng tip th cc sn phm v dch v tng t.</strong>&nbsp;i tc c th yu cu t chi nhn thng tin tip th bt c lc no bng cch yu cu ti&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mt.com/contact\">www.mt.com/contact</a>.  bit thm thng tin, vui lng xem chnh sch quyn ring t ca chng ti ti&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mt.com/privacypolicy\">www.mt.com/privacypolicy</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'iu khon &amp; iu kin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-04-14 17:01:55', '2024-04-14 17:01:55', '', 17, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=18', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
