(39, 1, '2024-04-18 06:06:39', '2024-04-18 06:06:39', '<h3><strong>i nt v thng hiu</strong></h3>\r\nPepsi l tp on a quc gia ni ting hin c tr s ti M chuyn sn xut v kinh doanh cc loi  ung, thc phm,... Vi kinh nghim lu i, cngdy chuyn sn xut hin i v ngun nguyn liu cht lng, cc sn phm ca Pepsico c ngi tiu dng a chung v la chn s dng hng u.\r\n<h3><strong>Thnh phn dinh dng trong sn phm</strong></h3>\r\nNc ung c ga hay nc ngt l ngun cung cp nng lng v ng di do cho c th. Ngoi ra sn phm cn b sung carbohydrate v natri. Theo thng tin c in r trn bao b sn phm, gi tr nng lng trung bnh trong 245ml nc ngt Pepsi khong 73.5 kcal.\r\n<h3><strong>Tc dng ca sn phm vi sc khe</strong></h3>\r\nMt s tc dng ni bt ca sn phm i vi sc khe nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cung cp nng lng</li>\r\n 	<li>B sung ng</li>\r\n 	<li>H tr h tiu ha</li>\r\n 	<li>Gim cm gic y bng, kh tiu</li>\r\n 	<li>...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Lu  khi s dng v cch bo qun sn phm</strong></h3>\r\nNc ngt c ga thng c bo qun  ni kh ro, thong mt, trnh t sn phm  ni c nhit  cao. Nc ngt s ngon hn khi bn dng lnh hoc dng vi . Trnh cm lon nc xc mnh.\r\n\r\nLu : Khng s dng khi bn d ng thnh phn sn phm, sn phm ht hn hoc c du hiu hng.\r\n<h3><strong>u im khi mua sn phm ti Marketo Shop</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"pb-[12px] text-[#222b45] max-h-auto\">\r\n<div class=\"text-14 leading-5\">\r\n\r\nDng sn phm nc git kht Pepsi ni ting hin ang c phn phi chnh hng ti Marketo Shop , m bo ng ngun gc xut x v an ton vi ngi s dng. Ngi dng c th mua sn phm online qua app hoc website  nhn c nhiu u i v khuyn mi mi ngy, cng dch v giao hng tn nh nhanh chng, tin li.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"w-full cursor-pointer pl-5px pt-2 text-center text-13 text-[#333] lg:text-14\"></div>', 'Nc ngt Pepsi Cola Sleek lon 245ml', 'Nc ngt ca thng hiu Pepsi an ton, cht lng c nh nh la chn tin dng. Nc ngt Pepsi Cola Sleek lon 245ml mang hng v c trng, thm ngon hp dn gip bn xua tan i cn kht ngay tc khc. Nc ngt Pepsi c ch bin theo cng ngh hin i, an ton cho sc khe ngi dng.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nuoc-ngot-pepsi-cola-sleek-lon-245ml', '', '', '2024-04-18 06:27:08', '2024-04-18 06:27:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=39', 0, 'product', '', 1),
