hi lng tng</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">340g</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">S lng</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">20 gi</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Khi lng l</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">17g</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">S dng</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">UNG NNG dng 1 gi pha vi 70-75ml nc nng.\nUNG LNH dng 2 gi pha vi 50-70ml nc nng v thm </div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">im ni bt</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">NesCaf t ho to ra mt th h c ph hon ton mi, kt hp hon ho gia c ph rang xay v c ph ho tan. Gi li trn vn hng thm c trng vi v m  kh cng</div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"mb-2 mt-3 lg:font-bold\">Bi vit sn phm</p>\n\n<div class=\"text-14 leading-5\">\n<h3><strong>i nt v thng hiu</strong></h3>\nRa mt ln u tin vo nm 1938 ti Thy S v tri qua nhiu bin c, Nescafe n nay  tr thnh mt trong nhngthng hiuc ph ha tan ni ting hng u th gii. Cc sn phm ca Nescafe u khng ch mang hng vthm ngon m cn gip ngi dng pha ch d dng v nhanh chng, tin li, an ton vi sc khe ca ngi tiu dng trn th trng th gii.\n<h3><strong>Thnh phn dinh dng ca sn phm</strong></h3>\nThnh phn chnh ca sn phm bao gm:Thnh phn: ng, bt kem pha c ph c cha sa (ng glucose, du thc vt, natri caseinate, c ph rang xay nhuyn (0.2%), mui), c ph ho tan (12%), maltodextrin, mui i-t, hng tng hp dng trong thc phm, cht iu chnh  chua 500(ii). Ngoi ra, trong100g c ph s cung cp cho c th khong 360 Kcal.\n<h3><strong>Tc dng ca sn phm vi sc khe</strong></h3>\nC ph ha tan Nescaf3 trong 1 m  hi ha,thm ngon kh cng. Ngoi ra, khng ch c v m  thm ngon, c ph cn mang n nhiu tc dng tt cho sc khe nh:\n<ul>\n 	<li>C ph en tt cho tr no v tng cng s tp trung.</li>\n 	<li>H tr t chy calo trong c th</li>\n 	<li>H tr qu trnh trao i cht din ra tt hn</li>\n 	<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Hng dn s dng</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Dng nng</strong>: Cho 1 gi c ph ha tan Nescafe 3 trong 1 m vo 70ml nc nng, khuy u v thng thc.</li>\n 	<li><strong>Dng lnh</strong>: Cho 2 gi c phha tan Nescafe 3 trong 1 m  vo 70ml nc nng, khuy u v cho thm  thng thc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Lu  khi s dng v cch bo qun sn phm</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Bo qun c ph ni kh ro, thong mt, trnh nh nng trc tip ca mt tri</li>\n 	<li>Khng nn ung qu nhiu c ph trong ngy s khin bn mt ng</li>\n 	<li>Khng s dng sn phm ht hoc c mi l</li>\n 	<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Cc mn n ngon vi sn phm</strong></h3>\nNgoi pha nhng ly c ph m , thm ngon, c ph ha tan Nescafe cn c th dng ch bin cc mn n khc l, c o nh:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Bnh flan c ph</li>\n 	<li>ng sng c ph</li>\n 	<li>Sa chua  c ph</li>\n 	<li>C ph nc ct da</li>\n 	<li></li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>', 'C ph sa NesCaf 3 in 1 m  hi ha 340g', 'C ph ha tan Nescafe l s kt hp hon ho gia c ph rang xay v c ph ha tan cng v sa thm bo ngt ngo cho ra ly c ph m . C ph ha tan Nescaf 3 trong 1 m  thm ngon cc cht, bng tnh c th cht v tinh thn, kch thch cc gic quan nng cao s tp trung cho bn.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '95-autosave-v1', '', '', '2024-04-19 14:42:11', '2024-04-19 14:42:11', '', 95, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=111', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
