(188, 1, '2024-04-21 09:26:43', '2024-04-21 09:26:43', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--1\"><strong>Trang web ca ti c cn chnh sch bo mt khng?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu trang web ca bn thu thp d liu t khch truy cp, hin th qung co v/hoc theo di khch truy cp thng qua phn tch, th chc chn trang web ca bn s cn c chnh sch bo mt.Nu a ch doanh nghip ca bn nm  EU v/hoc bn c k hoch kinh doanh vi khch hng  EU, th bn khng ch cn c chnh sch bo mt, M n cn cn phi tun th GDPR.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--2\"><strong>Chnh sch bo mt ca bn s bao gm nhng g?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chnh sch bo mt ca bn s bao gm gii thch v ba iu quan trng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Loi thng tin m bn thu thp</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cch thu thp cc thng tin ny</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cch thng tin c lu tr v bo v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--3\"><strong>C s khc bit trong cc loi thng tin c thu thp khng?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C  chnh sch bo mt phn bit gia thng tin c th nhn dng vi d liu khng ring t.Theo Vin Tiu chun v Cng ngh Quc gia M, thng tin nhn dng c nhn c nh ngha l:<em>Bt k thng tin no v mt c nhn c duy tr bi mt c quan, bao gm (1) bt k thng tin no c th c s dng  phn bit hoc theo di danh tnh ca c nhn, chng hn nh tn, s bo him x hi, ngy sinh v ni sinh, tn thi con gi ca m hoc h s sinh trc hc; v (2) bt k thng tin no khc c lin kt hoc c th lin kt vi mt c nhn, chng hn nh thng tin y t, gio dc, ti chnh v vic lm.</em>Trong khi , d liu khng ring t c nh ngha l:Thng tin c th tng ng vi mt ngi, ti khon hoc h s c th, nhng khng   xc nh, lin h hoc nh v ngi c lin quan n thng tin .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--4\"><strong>Vic ti khng xut bn Chnh sch bo mt trn trang web ca mnh c th gy ra bt k hu qu no khng?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C.Vic thu thp d liu m ngi dng khng bit l hnh vi phm ti c th b trng pht. Bn cn nu chnh xc loi thng tin m bn ang thu thp v thng xuyn cp nht chnh sch bo mt ca bn nu thng tin ny thay i. Nu khng, bn s phi i mt vi mc pht ng k l 20 triu Euro hoc 4% doanh thu ton cu ca bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--5\"><strong>Mu min ph v Chnh sch bo mt  Tun th Quy nh Chung v Bo v D liu (GDPR)</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti&nbsp;<strong>WebsitePlanet.com</strong>&nbsp;chng ti mun gip bn bt u &nbsp;<strong>v hy vng s gip bn tit kim c mt khon chi ph php l</strong>&nbsp; cho nn chng ti  chun b chnh sch bo mt mu nh sau. Bn c thoi mi ti n xung, chnh sa n, s dng n trn website ca bn, v chia s n vi bn b v ng nghip ca bn.<strong>Hy m bo sa i cc phn xut hin trong du ngoc m {  }, nhng ch m bn phi sa i trong mu  phn nh cc chi tit c th v website ca bn.</strong><strong>CHNG TI L NGI TT, NHNG CHNG TI KHNG PHI L LUT S V Y KHNG PHI L T VN PHP L. CHNH SCH BO MT MU NY L IM BT U V KHUNG SN CHO BN S DNG CNG VI CC LI KHUYN V IU CHNH T CC C VN PHP L C CHUYN MN V KINH NGHIM.</strong>Sau y l mt bn chnh sch bo mt mu m bn c th sa i v s dng cho ph hp vi cc nhu cu c th ca cng ty mnh  hy m bo tham kho  kin ca cc c vn php l c kinh nghim:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A. Gii thiu</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Quyn ring t ca khch truy cp website ca chng ti rt quan trng i vi chng ti v chng ti cam kt bo v n. Chnh sch ny gii thch nhng g chng ti s lm vi thng tin c nhn ca bn.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Vic ng  cho chng ti s dng cookie theo cc iu khon ca chnh sch ny khi bn truy cp website ca chng ti ln u s cho php chng ti s dng cookie mi khi bn truy cp website ca chng ti.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>B. Dn ngun</strong><br>Ti liu ny c to bng mt mu t SEQ Legal (seqlegal.com)<br>v c sa i bi Website Planet (<a href=\"https://www.websiteplanet.com/\">www.websiteplanet.com</a>)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>C. Thu thp thng tin c nhn</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cc loi thng tin c nhn sau y c th c thu thp, lu tr v s dng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin v my tnh ca bn bao gm a ch IP, v tr a l, loi v phin bn trnh duyt, h iu hnh;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin v cc lt truy cp v s dng website ny ca bn bao gm ngun gii thiu, thi lng truy cp, lt xem trang v ng dn iu hng website;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin chng hn nh a ch email m bn nhp khi ng k vi website ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin bn nhp khi to mt h s trn website ca chng tiv d nh tn, hnh nh h s, gii tnh, ngy sinh, tnh trng mi quan h, s thch v th vui, thng tin hc vn v thng tin cng vic;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin chng hn nh tn v a ch email m bn nhp  thit lp ng k nhn email v/hoc bn tin ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin m bn nhp trong khi s dng cc dch v trn website ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin c to trong khi s dng website ca chng ti, bao gm thi gian, tn sut v nhng trng hp bn s dng n;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin lin quan n bt c th g bn mua, cc dch v bn s dng hoc cc giao dch bn thc hin thng qua website ca chng ti, bao gm tn, a ch, s in thoi, a ch email v thng tin th tn dng ca bn;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin m bn ng ln website ca chng ti vi mc ch cng khai n trn internet, bao gm tn ngi dng, hnh nh h s v ni dung nhng bi ng ca bn;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thng tin c trong bt k lin lc no m bn gi cho chng ti bng email hoc thng qua website ca chng ti, bao gm ni dung lin lc v siu d liu ca n;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>bt k thng tin c nhn no khc m bn gi cho chng ti.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trc khi bn tit l cho chng ti thng tin c nhn ca ngi khc, bn phi c c s ng  ca ngi  i vi c vic tit l ln x l thng tin c nhn  theo chnh sch ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>D. S dng thng tin c nhn ca bn</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thng tin c nhn c gi cho chng ti thng qua website ca chng ti s c s dng cho cc mc ch c xc nh trong chnh sch ny hoc trn cc trang c lin quan ca website. Chng ti c th s dng thng tin c nhn ca bn cho nhng vic sau y:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>qun tr website v cng vic ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>c nhn ha website ca chng ti cho bn;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>cho php bn s dng cc dch v c sn trn website ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>gi cho bn sn phm c mua thng qua website ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>cung cp cc dch v c mua thng qua website ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>gi cc bo co, ha n, nhc nh thanh ton cho bn v thu cc khon thanh ton t bn;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>gi cho bn cc thng tin thng mi khng phi tip th;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>gi cho bn cc thng bo qua email m bn  yu cu c th;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>gi cho bn bn tin ca chng ti qua email, nu bn  yu cu n (bn c th thng bo cho chng ti bt c lc no nu bn khng c nhu cu nhn bn tin na);</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>gi cho bn cc thng tin tip th lin quan n doanh nghip ca chng ti hoc doanh nghip ca cc bn th ba c la chn cn thn m chng ti ngh rng c th bn quan tm qua ng bu in, ni bn  ng  c th v iu ny, hoc bng email hay cng ngh tng t (bn c th thng bo cho chng ti bt c lc no nu bn khng c nhu cu nhn cc thng tin tip th na);</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>cung cp cho cc bn th ba thng tin thng k v ngi dng ca chng ti (nhng cc bn th ba  s khng th nhn dng bt k ngi dng c nhn no t thng tin );</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>x l cc yu cu v khiu ni c thc hin bi hoc v bn lin quan n website ca chng ti;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>gi cho website ca chng ti bo mt v ngn chn gian ln;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>xc minh vic tun th cc iu khon v iu kin qun l vic s dng website ca chng ti (bao gm gim st cc tin nhn ring t c gi qua dch v nhn tin ring t trn website ca chng ti); v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>cc vic s dng khc.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu bn gi thng tin c nhn  ng ln website ca chng ti, chng ti s cng khai hoc s dng thng tin  theo s cho php m bn cp cho chng ti.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cc ci t ring t ca bn c th c s dng  gii hn vic cng khai thng tin ca bn trn website ca chng ti v c th c iu chnh bng cc kim sot quyn ring t trn website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chng ti s khng cung cp thng tin c nhn ca bn cho bt k bn th ba no  h hoc bt k bn th ba no khc tip th trc tip nu khng c s ng  r rng ca bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>E. Tit l thng tin c nhn</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chng ti c th tit l thng tin c nhn ca bn cho bt k nhn vin, cn b, nh bo him, c vn chuyn nghip, i l, nh cung cp hoc nh thu ph no khi thy cn thit hp l cho cc mc ch c nu trong chnh sch ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chng ti c th tit l thng tin c nhn ca bn cho bt k thnh vin no trong nhm cc cng ty ca chng ti (ngha l cc cng ty con ca chng ti, cng ty m ca chng ti v tt c cc cng ty con ca n) khi thy cn thit hp l cho cc mc ch c nu trong chnh sch ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chng ti c th tit l thng tin c nhn ca bn:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>n mc  m chng ti c yu cu phi lm nh vy theo php lut;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>lin quan n bt k th tc php l no ang hoc c th din ra trong tng lai;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li> thit lp, thc hin hoc bo v cc quyn hp php ca chng ti (bao gm vic cung cp thng tin cho ngi khc vi mc ch phng chng gian ln v gim ri ro tn dng);</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>cho ngi mua (hoc ngi mua tim nng) ca bt k doanh nghip hoc ti sn no m chng ti ang (hoc d tnh) bn; v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>cho bt k ai m chng ti kh tin tng c th np n ln mt ta n hoc c quan c thm quyn khc  yu cu tit l v thng tin c nhn  theo quan im hp l ca chng ti, ni ta n hoc c quan ny hu nh s c kh nng ra lnh tit l thng tin c nhn .</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tr khi c quy nh trong chnh sch ny, nu khng chng ti s khng cung cp thng tin c nhn ca bn cho cc bn th ba.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>F. Chuyn giao d liu quc t</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Thng tin m chng ti thu thp c th c lu tr, x l v chuyn giao gia bt k quc gia no ni chng ti hot ng  cho php chng ti s dng thng tin chiu theo chnh sch ny.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Thng tin m chng ti thu thp c th c chuyn giao n cc quc gia sau, ni khng c cc lut bo v d liu tng ng vi cc lut hin hnh trong Khu vc Kinh t chu u: Hoa K, Nga, Nht Bn, Trung Quc v n .</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Thng tin c nhn m bn cng khai trn website ca chng ti hoc gi  ng ln website ca chng ti c th c sn qua internet trn ton th gii. Chng ti khng th ngn chn vic nhng ngi khc s dng hoc lm dng thng tin .</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bn hon ton ng  vi vic chuyn giao thng tin c nhn c m t trong Mc F.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>G. Lu gi thng tin c nhn</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Mc G ny t ra cc chnh sch v th tc lu gi d liu ca chng ti, chng c thit k nhm gip m bo rng chng ti tun th cc ngha v php l ca mnh v vic lu gi v xa b thng tin c nhn.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Thng tin c nhn m chng ti x l cho bt k mc ch hoc cc mc ch no u s khng c gi li lu hn cn thit cho mc ch  hoc cc mc ch .</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Khng nh hng n iu G-2, chng ti thng s xa d liu c nhn thuc cc danh mc c lit k di y vo ngy/gi c nu bn di:<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"lower-alpha\"} -->\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>loi d liu c nhn s b xa {NHP NGY/GI}; v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>{NHP NGY/GI B SUNG}.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bt k cc quy nh khc ca Mc G ny, chng ti vn s gi li cc ti liu (bao gm c cc ti liu in t) c cha d liu c nhn:<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"lower-alpha\"} -->\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>n mc  m chng ti c yu cu phi lm nh vy theo php lut;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>nu chng ti tin rng cc ti liu  c th lin quan n bt k th tc php l no ang hoc c th din ra; v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li> thit lp, thc hin hoc bo v cc quyn hp php ca chng ti (bao gm vic cung cp thng tin cho ngi khc vi mc ch phng chng gian ln v gim ri ro tn dng).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>H. Bo mt thng tin c nhn ca bn</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Chng ti s thc hin cc bin php phng nga hp l v mt k thut v t chc  ngn chn tht thot, lm dng hoc thay i thng tin c nhn ca bn.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Chng ti s lu tr tt c thng tin c nhn m bn cung cp trn cc my ch (c bo v bng mt khu v tng la) bo mt ca chng ti.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tt c cc giao dch ti chnh in t c nhp thng qua website ca chng ti s c bo v bi cng ngh m ha.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bn chp nhn rng vic chuyn giao thng tin qua internet vn khng an ton v chng ti khng th m bo tnh bo mt ca d liu c gi qua internet.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bn c trch nhim gi kn mt khu m mnh s dng  truy cp website ca chng ti; chng ti s khng hi bn v mt khu ca bn (tr khi bn ng nhp vo website ca chng ti).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>I. Sa i</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chng ti c th cp nht chnh sch ny bt c lc no bng vic cng b mt phin bn mi trn website ca mnh. Thnh thong bn nn kim tra trang ny  m bo bn hiu ht mi thay i i vi chnh sch ny. Chng ti c th thng bo cho bn v nhng thay i trong chnh sch ny bng email hoc thng qua h thng nhn tin ring trn website ca chng ti.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>J. Quyn ca bn</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn c th hng dn chng ti cung cp cho bn bt k thng tin c nhn no m chng ti nm gi v bn; vic cung cp thng tin  s phi tun theo cc iu sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>thanh ton mt khon ph {NHP PH NU PH HP}; v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>cung cp bng chng thch hp v danh tnh ca bn ({IU CHNH VN BN PHN NH CHNH SCH CA BN cho mc ch ny, chng ti thng s chp nhn mt bn sao h chiu ca bn c chng nhn bi mt cng chng vin cng vi bn gc ca mt ha n tin ch c ghi r a ch hin ti ca bn}).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chng ti c th t chi cung cp thng tin c nhn m bn yu cu trong phm vi php lut cho php.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn c th hng dn chng ti vo bt c lc no khng c s dng thng tin c nhn ca bn cho cc mc ch tip th.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trn thc t, bn thng s ng  trc mt cch r rng vi vic chng ti s dng thng tin c nhn ca bn cho cc mc ch tip th, hoc chng ti s cho bn c hi t chi vic s dng thng tin c nhn ca bn cho cc mc ch tip th.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>K. Website ca bn th ba</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Website ca chng ti bao gm cc siu lin kt n v thng tin chi tit v cc website ca bn th ba. Chng ti khng kim sot v khng chu trch nhim i vi cc chnh sch v thc hnh v quyn ring t ca cc bn th ba.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>L. Cp nht thng tin</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vui lng cho chng ti bit nu thng tin c nhn m chng ti lu gi v bn cn c sa cha hoc cp nht.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>M. Cookie</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Website ca chng ti s dng cookie. Mt cookie l mt tp c cha m nh danh (mt chui cc k t v s) c mt my ch web gi ti mt trnh duyt web v c trnh duyt ny lu tr. M nh danh sau  c gi tr li my ch mi khi trnh duyt yu cu mt trang t my ch. Cookie c th l cookie di hn hoc cookie theo phin: mt cookie di hn s c mt trnh duyt web lu tr v s cn hiu lc cho n ngy n ht hn, tr phi b ngi dng xa trc ngy ht hn; mt khc, mt cookie theo phin s ht hn vo cui phin ca ngi dng, khi trnh duyt web b ng. Cc cookie thng khng cha bt k thng tin no nhn dng ch danh mt ngi dng, nhng thng tin c nhn m chng ti lu tr v bn c th c lin kt n thng tin c lu tr v ly t cc cookie. {CHN CM T CHNH XC Chng ti ch s dng cookie theo phin / ch s dng cookie di hn / s dng c cookie theo phin ln cookie di hn trn website ca chng ti.}</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tn ca cc cookie m chng ti s dng trn website ca mnh v cc mc ch m chng c s dng c nu ra di y:<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"lower-alpha\"} -->\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>chng ti s dng Google Analytics v Adwords trn website ca mnh  nhn ra mt my tnh khi mt ngi dng {BAO GM TT C VIC S DNG CA CC COOKIE  TRN WEBSITE CA BN truy cp website / theo di ngi dng khi h iu hng website / cho php s dng gi hng trn website / ci thin tnh kh dng ca website / phn tch vic s dng website / qun tr website / ngn nga gian ln v ci thin tnh bo mt ca website / c nhn ha website cho tng ngi dng / nhm mc tiu cc qung co c th l s thch c bit i vi nhng ngi dng c th / m t (cc) mc ch};</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Hu ht trnh duyt cho php bn t chi chp nhn cookiev d:<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"lower-alpha\"} -->\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>trong Internet Explorer (phin bn 10), bn c th chn cc cookie bng cch s dng ci t ghi  x l cookie c sn khi nhp vo Tools (Cng c), Internet Options (Ty chn Internet), Privacy (Quyn ring t) v Advanced (Nng cao);</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>trong Firefox (phin bn 24), bn c th chn tt c cookie bng cch nhp vo Tools, Options, Privacy, chn Use custom settings for history (S dng ci t ty chnh cho lch s) t trnh n th xung v b chn Accept cookies from sites (Chp nhn cookie t cc website); v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>trong Chrome (phin bn 29), bn c th chn tt c cc cookie bng cch truy cp trnh n Customize and control (Ty chnh v kim sot) ri nhp vo Settings (Ci t), Show advanced settings (Hin th ci t nng cao) v Content settings (Ci t ni dung), sau  chn Block sites from setting any data (Chn cc website ci t bt k d liu no) bn di tiu  Cookies.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vic chn tt c cc cookie s c tc ng tiu cc n tnh kh dng ca nhiu website. Nu bn chn cookie, bn s khng th s dng mi tnh nng trn website ca chng ti.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":3} -->\n<ol start=\"3\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bn c th xa cc cookie  c lu tr trn my tnh ca mnhv d:<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"lower-alpha\"} -->\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:lower-alpha\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>trong Internet Explorer (phin bn 10), bn phi xa th cng cc tp cookie (bn c th tm thy hng dn  lm iu  ti<a href=\"http://support.microsoft.com/kb/278835\">http://support.microsoft.com/kb/278835</a>);</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>trong Firefox (phin bn 24), bn c th xa cc cookie bng cch nhp vo Tools, Options v Privacy, sau  chn Use custom settings for history, nhp vo Show Cookies (Hin th cookie), sau  nhp vo Remove All Cookies (Xa tt c cookie); v</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>trong Chrome (phin bn 29), bn c th xa tt c cookie bng cch truy cp trnh n Customize and control v nhp vo Settings, Show advanced settings v Clear browsing data (Xa d liu duyt web), sau  chn Delete cookies and other site and plug-in data (Xa cc cookie v d liu trnh cm v website khc) trc khi nhp vo Clear browsing data.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Vic xa cookie s c tc ng tiu cc n tnh kh dng ca nhiu website.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Website Planet khng chu bt k trch nhim php l no v khuyn bn nn tham kho  kin cc chuyn gia php l nu bn ang trin khai mu trn cho website ca mnh.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--6\">GDPR l g?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Quy nh v Bo v D liu Chung (GDPR) l mt b lut c lp ra  bo v d liu c nhn ca cc cng dn Lin minh chu u (EU). Hi ng Lin minh chu u, Ngh vin chu u v y ban chu u  hp tc  gip ngi dn kim sot tt hn cc d liu c nhn ca h.c Ngh vin chu u chnh thc thng qua vo nm 2016, EU cho php mt giai on n hn hai nm  cc cng ty v t chc tun th cc quy nh mi. Do , k t ngy 25 thng 05 nm 2018, bt k doanh nghip no khng tun th cc lut GDPR mi s vi phm lut php.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--7\">Ai b nh hng bi GDPR?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bt k doanh nghip no hot ng trong EU v bt k cng ty no hot ng kinh doanh, hoc c hy vng lm kinh doanh, vi cc cng dn ca Lin minh chu u phi tun th cc lut mi. Ngay c cc cng ty bn ngoi EU cng b nh hng nu h cung cp hng ha hoc dch v cho cng dn EU, v bt c ai nm gi d liu c nhn ca cng dn EU u c th b pht k t ngy 25 thng 05 nm 2018.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--8\">Loi D liu No Ri vo GDPR?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bt k thng tin no c phn loi l cc thng tin chi tit c nhn c th c s dng  xc nh mt cng dn EU u c bo v bi GDPR v bao gm, nhng khng gii hn, cc d liu sau:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Hnh nh</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>a ch email</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cc bi ng trn cc phng tin truyn thng x hi</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Thng tin y t c nhn</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cc a ch IP</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Thng tin ngn hng</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tr v thnh nin khng th t cho php s dng hp php d liu c nhn ca mnh; do , cha m hoc ngi gim h ca tr t 16 tui tr xung phi c xin php trc khi mt cng ty c th s dng d liu ca tr v thnh nin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--9\">Ti sao cc Cng ty nn Tun th GDPR?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bt k doanh nghip no khng tun th GDPR k t ngy 25 thng 05 s phi chu mc pht nng ca EU ln ti 4% hoc 20 triu Euro doanh thu ton cu, ty theo ci no cao nht. V cn c nhiu hnh pht nng hn na, ty thuc vo s vi phm.C l quan trng hn, cc cng ty khng tun th cc lut mi s phi i mt vi s mt uy tn trn th trng. Ni cch khc, vic tun th cc lut ca GDPR gip to nim tin ni khch hng ca cng ty v khch truy cp vo website ca h. Mt khi cng chng cm thy an ton, h cng sn sng lm vic vi t chc . Vic tun th GDPR khng ch l lut  n l mt vic lm tt.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--10\">Chuyn g s Xy ra Nu c Vi phm D liu?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu c mt vi phm d liu,  l khi mt ngi ngoi c c truy cp vo d liu ca mt c nhn m khng c php, GDPR yu cu cc cng ty thng bo cho cc c quan bo v d liu thch hp trong vng 72 gi. Cng ty cng phi thng bo cho cc c nhn b nh hng cng nhanh cng tt. iu quan trng cn lu , mc tiu chnh ca GDPR l bo v thng tin c nhn ca ngi dng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"hselect--11\">Cc Chnh sch Bo mt Mi s Nh th no?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By gi bn  hiu lp lun ca cc lut v mt s vn  c bn ca cc lut , sau y l mt s hng dn  bn vit cho mnh mt chnh sch bo mt theo cch tun th GDPR:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>m bo chnh sch ngn gn v sc tch.</strong>Chnh sch bo mt phi c ba yu t c bn: phi sc tch v d tip cn; phi c vit r rng bng ngn ng n gin m ngay c mt a tr cng c th hiu c; v phi min ph.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Gii thch vic s dng d liu ca bn.</strong>M t nhng g bn s lm vi d liu mt khi bn thu thp n. V d: cho bit liu bn s s dng n cho cc mc ch tip th hoc bn cho cc bn th ba hay khng.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Gii thch vic s dng cookie ca bn.</strong>Nu bn s dng cookie cho qung co hnh vi trc tuyn, theo di s thch v thi quen trc tuyn ca khch truy cp, bn s cn  cho khch truy cp website ca bn bit.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Minh bch v chia s d liu vi cc bn th ba.</strong>Nu r vi ngi no bn s chia s d liu  thu thp c v cho mc ch g. Mc d ng lut khi chia s thng tin ca cc c nhn vi, c th k ra mt vi i tng nh kim ton vin, mng x hi, v cc nh cung cp dch v khch hng, vic ny s l bt hp php nu nh khng thng bo cho khch truy cp website ca bn.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>5. Gii thch cc quyn ca c nhn.</strong>Bn bt buc phi gii thch nhng quyn ring t no m khch truy cp c. Cc quyn ca h bao gm nh sau:</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>H c th yu cu xa hoc sa d liu ca h</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>H c th truy cp d liu m mt cng ty c v h</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>H c th yu cu chuyn d li