(208, 1, '2024-04-21 10:16:24', '2024-04-21 10:16:24', '<table class=\"mt-3 text-14 leading-5\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Thng hiu</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">Kronenbourg 1664 Blanc (Php)</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Sn xut ti</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">Vit Nam</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Loi sn phm</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">Bia cc loi</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Nng  cn</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">5%</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Th tch</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">330ml</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Thnh phn</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">Nc, i mch, la m, siro ng, hoa bia, hng caramen t nhin, hng v cam t nhin</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">ng gi</td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">Lon</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Lu </td>\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\n<div class=\"text-justify\">Sn phm dnh cho ngi trn 18 tui v khng dnh cho ph n mang thai. Thng thc c trch nhim,  ung  ung c cn th khng li xe!</div></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"mb-2 mt-3 lg:font-bold\">Bi vit sn phm</p>\n\n<div class=\"text-14 leading-5\">\n<h3><strong>i nt v thng hiu</strong></h3>\n166 Blanc l mt thng hiu bia ni ting, c sn xut b Pelforth, mt cng ty bia hng u ti Php. Bia 1664 Blanc mang n cho ngi ung nhng tri nghim tuyt vi vi hng v ti mt v phong cch hon ton ring bit. Vi mu sc trng c v hng thm phc hp ca cam, chanh v cc loi gia v, 1664 Blanc l s la chn hon ho cho nhng ai yu thch bia thch hp trong cc dp hp mt bn b, tic tng hay thng thc mt ba n ngon. Vi s kt hp tinh t gia truyn thng v s i mi, 1664 Blanc l mt thng hiu bia ng  khm ph v tri nghim.\n<h3><strong>Thnh phn dinh dng trong sn phm</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Thnh phn bia gm nc, i mch, la m, siro ng, hoa bia, hng caramen t nhin, hng v cam t nhin</li>\n 	<li>Bia c nng  5%, hng cam qut c trng v v cay nh</li>\n 	<li>Mi lon 330ml cung cp nng lng khong 150 calo</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Tc dng ca sn phm vi sc khe</strong></h3>\nUng bia vi lng va phi hp l s mang n mt s li ch cho c th nh:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Gip tinh thn th gin, cm cng thng mt mi</li>\n 	<li>Ci thin chc nng tim mch, lu thng tt hn, phng nga x va ng mch</li>\n 	<li>Ci thin chc nng no b</li>\n 	<li>Chc khe xng</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Lu  khi s dng v cch bo qun sn phm</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li> ni kh ro thong mt, trnh nhit  cao, nh nng trc tip, trnh b ng </li>\n 	<li>Cn thn ri v</li>\n 	<li>Khng ung bia khi bng i</li>\n 	<li>Khng li xe sau khi s dng</li>\n 	<li>Khng dng cho ph n c thai, ngi di 18 tui</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>\nCc mn n ngon vi sn phm</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>G hp bia</li>\n 	<li>Hi sn hp bia</li>\n 	<li>M xo bia, s ip nng bia</li>\n 	<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>u im khi mua sn phm ti Bch ho XANH</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Sn phm ti Bch ha XANH m bo chnh hng cht lng t nhng nh sn xut ni ting trong v ngoi nc</li>\n 	<li>Gi bn tt, thng xuyn c nhiu chng trnh u i hp dn</li>\n 	<li>D dng t hng online qua app v web Bch ha XANH, giao tn nh nhanh chng, tin li</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;', 'Bia Blanc 1664 lon 330ml', '<p>Tinh ty bia Php t nm 1664. Bia 1664 Blanc sn xut trn dy chuyn hin i cng b quyt nu bia tuyt ho cho cm gic ung sng khoi y thch th. Bia lon tin dng, thit k hin i, 24 lon bia Blanc 1664 330ml dng thng tit kim hn cho nhng cuc vui ko di</p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '190-autosave-v1', '', '', '2024-04-21 10:16:24', '2024-04-21 10:16:24', '', 190, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=208', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
