s=\"mb-2 mt-3 lg:font-bold\">Bi vit sn phm</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text-14 leading-5\">\r\n<h3><strong>i nt v thng hiu Twister</strong></h3>\r\nTwister l thng hiu chuyn sn xut v phn phi cc sn phm nc tri cy hng u ti Vit Nam, c sn xut bi Cng ty TNHH Nc gii kht Suntory PepsiCo Vit Nam, theo bn quyn ca Tropicana Products.\r\n<h3><strong>Thnh phn dinh dng trong sn phm</strong></h3>\r\nL sn phm nc p tri cy c v cam hp dn, nc cam p Twister c cha nhng thnh phn dinh dng nh: Nng lng, carbohydrate, ng, natri, sodium, v cc Vitamin C, A. Trong , theo thng tin trn bao b sn phm th trong 100ml nc cam p Twister c cha khong 52.5 kcal.\r\n<h3><strong>Tc dng ca sn phm vi sc khe</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Khng nhng l sn phm gip gii kht thng thng m nc cam p Twister Tropicana cn b sung cho c th cc loi Vitamin cn thit nh: Vitamin A, Vitamin C. Gip cung cp nng lng, tng cng th lc, lm chm qu trnh lo ha da.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nc p Twister vi ngun nguyn liu t nhin c la chn cn thn kt hp cng ngh sn xut hin i, mang li thc ung c hng v thm ngon, tt cho sc khe. Khi thng thc nc cam p Twister gip xua tan mi cm gic mt mi, cng thng ngay tc th, em li cm gic thoi mi nht cho bn sau mi ln s dng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Lu  khi s dng v cch bo qun sn phm</strong></h3>\r\nHng v: Twister Cam c thnh phn ch yu t nc ct cam t nhin, v ngt thanh mt cng hng thm t nhin trong tng tp cam ti, mang li cm gic sng khoi, ti mi.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Thit k: Chai 450ml</li>\r\n 	<li>HSD: 06 thng k t ngy sn xut Ngon hn khi ung lnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bo qun ni sch s, kh ro thong mt, trnh nh nng mt tri.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nn lc u sn phm trc khi s dng, sau khi m np nn  trong ngn mt t lnh v dng ht trong vng 3 ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>u im khi mua sn phm ti Bch ho XANH</strong></h3>\r\nBch ha XANH l a ch bn hng uy tn, by bn a dng nhng sn phm chnh hng t nhiu thng hiu ni ting. Ngoi ra khi mua hng trc tuyn ti trang www.bachhoaxanh.com hoc  ng dng Bch ha XANH trn in thoi, bn s nhn c nhiu chng trnh u i hp dn, cng dch v giao hng nhanh chng t