ang ncho ngi tiu dng nhng gi c ph t chun cht lng tt nht, cngnhiu u i mi mi ngy v dch v giao hng tn ni, nhanh chng.\r\n<strong>Xem thm:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/1-goi-ca-phe-nescafe-bao-nhieu-calo-cach-uong-ca-phe-giam-can-hieu-qua-1388996\">1 gi Nescafe c bao nhiu calo? Cch ung c ph gim cn hiu qu</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/nescafe-co-nhung-loai-ca-phe-hoa-tan-nao-ban-da-thu-chua-1401577\">Nescafe c nhng loi c ph ha tan no, bn  th cha</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'C ph en  NesCaf Caf Vit Arabica & Robusta 192g', '<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/ca-phe-hoa-tan\">C ph ha tan</a>m  hi ha gia c ph Robusta v Arabica. Bng sn phm<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/ca-phe-hoa-tan/ca-phe-den-nescafe-robusta-arabica-cafe-viet-192g\">c ph en  NesCaf Caf Vit Arabica &amp; Robusta 192g</a>t 100% c ph ho hng tuyn chn t vng c ph ni ting c nc<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/ca-phe-hoa-tan-nescafe\">c ph ha tan NesCaf</a>mang n ly c ph en thun ty Vit Nam mnh m, li cun', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ca-phe-den-da-nescafe-cafe-viet-arabica-robusta-192g', '', '', '2024-04-22 04:23:49', '2024-04-22 04:23:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=321', 0, 'product', '', 0),
