rong c ph sa gip ngn nga cc bnh tim mch v bnh Parkinson,</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Lu  khi s dng v cch bo qun sn phm</strong></h3>\r\nSn phm vi thit k dng gi nh tin li, c th em theo trong ba l, ti xch, v rt d bo qun.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bo qun c ph  ni kh thong.</li>\r\n 	<li>1 gi c ph pha vi 75ml nc nng khuy u v thng thc</li>\r\n 	<li>Dng 2 gi nu ung vi  lnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nn dng ngay sau khi m gi sn phm.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ch nn s dng lng va  c ph mi ngy, khng nn lm dng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>u im khi mua sn phm ti Bch ho XANH</strong></h3>\r\nCc sn phm chnh hng ca Trung Nguyn c th d dng tm mua ti cc ca hng Bch ha XANH trn ton quc. Bch ha XANH ch kinh doanh hng ha c ngun gc r rng, nn bn c th an tm mua hng ti y.\r\n\r\nNgoi ra, bn c th t hng ti www.bachhoaxanh.com hoc trn ng dng Bch ha XANH trn in thoi  c giao hng nhanh chng tn nh cng nhiu u i hp dn.\r\n\r\n&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/trung-nguyen-co-nhung-loai-ca-phe-hoa-tan-nao-loai-nao-ngon-nhat-1401913\">Trung Nguyn c nhng loi c ph ha tan no? Loi no ngon nht?</a>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'C ph ha tan Trung Nguyn Legend Classic 204g', 'Hng c ph xay c trng, th cht mnh cng v ng m pha ln cht ngt bi y bn sc,mang n nhng ngi am mc phmt loic ph ha tancht lng cao cung cp nng lng khi dy hng khi', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ca-phe-hoa-tan-trung-nguyen-legend-classic-204g', '', '', '2024-04-22 04:25:07', '2024-04-22 04:25:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=329', 0, 'product', '', 0),
