ip, nn p lnh trc khi ung</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"whitespace-nowrap border-2 border-[#f1f1f1] bg-[#f4f6f9] px-4 py-2 align-top\">Bo qun</td>\r\n<td class=\"w-full border-2 border-DEFAULT px-4 py-2\">\r\n<div class=\"text-justify\"> ni kh ro, thong mt, trnh tip xc trc tip vi nh nng mt tri</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"mb-2 mt-3 lg:font-bold\">Bi vit sn phm</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text-14 leading-5\">Ru tri cy ngy nay cng dn tr nn ph bin v tr thnh thc ung a thch ca nhiu ngi. Nm bt c xu hng  nhiu n v sn xut  ung  lin tc cho ra mt nhng sn phm ru tri cy mi l trong  c<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/ruou-ngon-cac-loai-mg-spirit\">ru MG Spirit</a>- thng hiu ru nhp khu t Ty Ban Nha.\r\n\r\nMG Spirit hin ang c 8 dng sn phm ru tri cy vi 8 hng v khc nhau. Trong  ni bt c<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/ruou-ngon-cac-loai/ruou-mg-spirit-vodka-pineapple-huong-dua-55-275ml\">Ru MG Spirit Vodka Pineapple hng da 5.5% 275ml\r\n</a>\r\nSn phml s kt hp c o gia v ru mnh Vodka cng v chua ngt ca dacho cm gic thng thc mi l, khoan khoi, d chu.  l cht nng ca ru ha quyn thm v thanh ngt ca da to ra hng v pha trn kh qun.\r\n\r\n\r\nSn phm c nng  cn nh 5.5% cho cm gic ung d chu, khng qu gay gt, ph hp cho nhiu i tng bao gm ph n v ngi c tu lng thp.\r\n\r\nD vy nhng sn phm ny l<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/ruou-ngon-cac-loai\">ru</a>c cha cn nn hy chn ung mt cch c trch nhim, khng li xe khi  s dng bn nh.\r\n\r\nTham kho ngay<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/nhung-loai-trai-cay-giup-giai-ruou-nhanh-chong-ma-hieu-qua-975044\">nhng loi tri cy gip gii ru nhanh chng m hiu qu</a>. Lu li ngay, bn s cn n khi qu chn trong nhng cuc vui.</div>', 'Ru MG Spirit Vodka Pineapple hng da 5.5% chai 275ml', 'Ru ngon ho hng t thng hiu MG Spirit.Ru MG Spirit Vodka Pineapple hng da 5.5% 275mls kt hp c o gia v ru mnh Vodka cng v chua ngt ca dacho cm gic thng thc mi l t cht nng ca ru v hng da thanh ngt cho cm gic khoan khoi, d chu', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ruou-mg-spirit-vodka-pineapple-huong-dua-5-5-chai-275ml', '', '', '2024-04-22 03:58:52', '2024-04-22 03:58:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=409', 0, 'product', '', 0),
