it  cao.</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"mb-2 mt-3 lg:font-bold\">Bi vit sn phm</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text-14 leading-5\">\r\n<h2><strong>Tr tri cy Cozy: thm ngon hp dn - gii kht tuyt vi</strong></h2>\r\nNhng ai  thng thc qua cc sn phmnc trCozy chc hn rt n tng vi gi thnh r m tr li rt cht lng. Mi y, thng hiu Cozy va cho ra mt b ba tr tri cy Cozy vi bao b gn nh, bt mt vi hng v tr thm ngon, va ming.\r\n<div></div>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/nuoc-tra/tra-vai-cozy-225ml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tr vi Cozy 255ml</a>l sn phm nc tr ng hp mi ra mt gn y v to nn mt cn st trong th trng nc gii kht. Sn phm c dung tch 255ml ng gi trong hp giy vi np nha tin li, d mang theo cho bn thng thc mi ni. Tr vi Cozy mang hng v thm ngon t nhng l tr xanh ha quyn vi v ngt va vn, thm mi vi ti mi, cho bn mt sn phm nc tr vi gii kht d dng m thm ngon khng thua g cc qun. Tr xanh cha nhiu cht chng oxy ha gip bn c mt ngy nng ng, ti tr.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Hng dn s dng</strong>: Lc u sn phm trc khi dng, ngon hn khi ung lnh.  tr c m v v hp dn hn, bn c th cho thm tri cy nh vi ng hp  thng thc cng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Cng xem chi tit review v sn phm tr tri cy Cozy ca Bch Ha Xanh ti y:<a href=\"https://www.bachhoaxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/review-chi-tiet-tra-trai-cay-dong-hop-cozy-moi-voi-3-huong-vi-cuc-ngon-1253313\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Review chi tit 3 hng v hp dn mi ca tr tri cy Cozy</a></strong>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Tr vi Cozy 225ml', 'Mang hng v thm ngon t nhng l tr xanh ha quyn vi v ngt va vn, thm mi vi ti mi, cho bn mt sn phm nc tr vi gii kht d dng m thm ngon khng thua g cc qun. Tr xanh cha nhiu cht chng oxy ha gip bn c mt ngy nng ng, ti tr.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tra-vai-cozy-225ml', '', '', '2024-04-26 09:21:15', '2024-04-26 09:21:15', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=416', 0, 'product', '', 0),
